text: Nelson Hayford Lincoln was a sports shooter from USA. Lincoln competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born on 20 April 1914 and died on 7 March 2000.Nelson Lincoln == References == Category:1914 births Category:2000 deaths Category:American sport shooters Category:Olympians for the United States Category:Sportspeople from Massachusetts Category:People from Medford, Massachusetts
